Now consider the latitude of the cusps. During periods of southward IMF, enhanced reconnection rates on the dayside equatorial magnetopause cause the cusps to move ‚àº10‚àò\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
				\usepackage{amsmath}
				\usepackage{wasysym}
				\usepackage{amsfonts}
				\usepackage{amssymb}
				\usepackage{amsbsy}
				\usepackage{mathrsfs}
