				\setlength{\oddsidemargin}{-69pt}
				\begin{document}$10~\mbox{cm}^{-3}$\end{document}. The overall chemical composition of ICMEs resembles that of the slow solar wind, but the He density is frequently enhanced, with the ratio of He to proton densities often exceeding 8% and sometimes exceeding 10%. Minor ions with Z>2\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
